profile: With professional, dedicated plumbing service to all major cities and surrounding areas in Alberta, and with some of the best plumbers in the industry, The Gentlemen Plumbers work hard to exceed your expectations and deliver quality. If you need a plumber, call us today for plumbing or heating issues, leaky sinks and faucets, clogged drains, toilet, bathtub and shower repairs, furnace cleaning and repairs, hot water tanks and tankless hot water heaters, furnace installation and maintenance, trenchless pipe repair, camera sewer inspection, and more! We have local branches in Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, and Medicine Hat, with extended service all over Southern Alberta, including Camrose, Sherwood Park, St. Albert, Airdrie, High River, Crossfield, Carstairs, Olds, Innisfail, Wetaskiwin, Leduc, Lacombe, Okotoks, Nanton, Taber, Cardston, Didsbury, Brooks, Crowsnest Pass, Cochrane, Strathmore, Sundre, Three Hills, Ponoka, Fort Macleod, Pincher Creek, Bowden, Fort Saskatchewan, Chestermere, Sylvan Lake, Spruce Grove, and Stony Plain.

profile: At 24/7 Electric, we are here to set the example of what to expect when you hire an Electrician. It is our goal to be the authority on ethics and electrical code in the residential service industry. Our strength is our passion to provide honest quality work to our customers. We achieve this by employing educated, experienced staff who are as passionate as we are. Our staff are trained for their specific division and work to be experts in that field. That dedication has been the success of our growing loyalty program, the referrals and repeat business we receive from our customers. With our trained staff we are also equipped to take on all of our customers' home servicing needs; from repairing a light switch to the electrical needs of a complete home renovation.

profile:
BAMJ Electric and Controls, Help to Power the Future
BAMJ Electric and Controls: We can make it happen. 
Whether it’s industrial, commercial, or residential electrical services in Calgary, consider it done. 
Our electricians are known for our positive work ethic, top-notch customer service and 24/7 emergency services. 

Electrical work can be daunting but it doesn’t have to be.  
We know you just want to get your problem fixed and trust your electrician. 
Our electricians are here for you: simple renovation designs, technical troubleshooting, commissioning and maintenance.  

If your company is looking into an upgrade, our specialists can assist and guide you in a variety of ways from the designing and planning stages to the final installation and implementation; including PLC program conversions to industry standard processors you will be upgrading to.

If your electrical project needs are lacking or need a change, we can provide you with an onsite quote and design ideas that meet all the codes and standards. 

No dream is unattainable!
